COMBINE taco sauce, sugar, liquid smoke and onion in medium saucepan. Cook over medium heat, stirring constantly, for 10 minutes. Cool slightly; store tightly covered in refrigerator. MICROWAVE METHOD: COMBINE taco sauce, sugar, liquid smoke and onion in medium, microwave-safe bowl. Microwave on HIGH (100%) power for 2 to 3 minutes, stirring every minute. Cool slightly; store tightly covered in refrigerator.